ss an extension of hypothetical improved upper time-bounds\nfor APSP in non-negatively edge-weighted DAGs to include directed graphs with a\npolynomial number of large directed cycles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 7 Aug 2021 14:21:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-10"}
